title: (Minister for Children, Equality, Disability, Integration and Youth) Order 2024.
heading: 1. This Order may be cited as the Appointment of Special Advisers
text_raw:
1. This Order may be cited as the Appointment of Special Advisers 
(Minister for Children, Equality, Disability, Integration and Youth) Order 2024.

title: (Minister for Children, Equality, Disability, Integration and Youth) Order 2024.
heading: 2. Tom Sheppard, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the
text_raw:
2. Tom Sheppard, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the 
offices of the Department of Children, Equality, Disability, Integration and 
Youth, is appointed to be a Special Adviser to the Minister for Children, Equality, 
Disability, Integration and Youth with effect from 9 April 2024.
text_norm: 2 tom sheppard particular whose address deposited office department child equality disability integration youth appointed special adviser minister child equality disability integration youth effect 9 april 2024

title: (Minister for Children, Equality, Disability, Integration and Youth) Order 2024.
heading: 3. Eoin Wilson, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the
text_raw:
3. Eoin Wilson, particulars of whose address have been deposited at the 
offices of the Department of Children, Equality, Disability, Integration and 
Youth, is appointed to be a Special Adviser to the Minister for Children, Equality, 
Disability, Integration and Youth with effect from 9 April 2024. 

GIVEN under the Official Seal of the Government, 

3 June, 2024. 

SIMON HARRIS, 

Taoiseach. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 21st June, 2024.
